      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's... that's a really harsh way to put it. I didn't realize it was so obvious to her. It just feels like there's no way to win. Whether I try to keep going or I just sit here and wait for things to get worse, someone always ends up paying for it. It feels like a constant cycle of making things harder for everyone I love.",
